  "description": "Console one-click approval (POST /webhook/console-approve, recommendation_id): send customer email, mark approved, advance lead to consultation_offered, create 2-day follow-up, audit. WF4 approve-branch without the Gmail wait (the console click is the approval). Customer email is routed to the operator inbox for the synthetic demo.",
  "settings": { "executionOrder": "v1", "availableInMCP": true },
